            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:1</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Why standest thou afar off, O LORD? why hidest thou thyself in times of trouble?</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Why, Jehovah, dost Thou stand at a distance? Thou dost hide in times of adversity,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Why standest<S>5975</S> thou afar off<S>7350</S>, O Jehovah<S>3068</S>? Why hidest<S>5956</S> thou thyself in times<S>6256</S> of trouble<S>6869</S>?</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Why do you stand far off, Yahweh? Why do you hide yourself in times of trouble? </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:2</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The wicked in his pride doth persecute the poor: let them be taken in the devices that they have imagined.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Through the pride of the wicked, Is the poor inflamed, They are caught in devices that they devised.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">In the pride<S>1346</S> of the wicked<S>7563</S> the poor<S>6041</S> is hotly pursued<S>1814</S>; Let them be taken<S>8610</S> in the devices<S>4209</S> that<S>2098</S> they have conceived<S>2803</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">In arrogance, the wicked hunt down the weak. They are caught in the schemes that they devise. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:3</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">For the wicked boasteth of his heart’s desire, and blesseth the covetous, whom the LORD abhorreth.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Because the wicked hath boasted Of the desire of his soul, And a dishonest gainer he hath blessed, He hath despised Jehovah.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">For the wicked<S>7563</S> boasteth<S>1984</S> of his heart<S>5315</S>'s desire<S>8378</S>, And the covetous<S>1214</S> renounceth<S>1288</S>, yea<S>5006</S>, contemneth Jehovah<S>3068</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">For the wicked boasts of his heart’s cravings. He blesses the greedy, and condemns Yahweh. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:4</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The wicked, through the pride of his countenance, will not seek after God: God is not in all his thoughts.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The wicked according to the height of his face, inquireth not. 'God is not!' [are] all his devices.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The wicked<S>7563</S>, in the pride<S>1363</S> of his countenance<S>639</S>, saith<S>1875</S>, He will not require it<S>4209</S>. All his thoughts are<S>430</S>, There is no God.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The wicked, in the pride of his face, has no room in his thoughts for God. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:5</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His ways are always grievous; thy judgments are far above out of his sight: as for all his enemies, he puffeth at them.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Pain do his ways at all times, On high [are] Thy judgments before him, All his adversaries -- he puffeth at them.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His ways<S>1870</S> are firm<S>2342</S> at all times<S>6256</S>; Thy judgments<S>4941</S> are far above<S>4791</S> out of his sight<S>6887</S>: As for all his adversaries, he puffeth at them<S>6315</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His ways are prosperous at all times. He is haughty, and your laws are far from his sight. As for all his adversaries, he sneers at them. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:6</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He hath said in his heart, I shall not be moved: for I shall never be in adversity.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He hath said in his heart, 'I am not moved,' To generation and generation not in evil.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He saith<S>559</S> in his heart<S>3820</S>, I shall not be moved<S>4131</S>; To all generations<S>1755</S> I shall not be in adversity<S>7451</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He says in his heart, “I shall not be shaken. For generations I shall have no trouble.” </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:7</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His mouth is full of cursing and deceit and fraud: under his tongue is mischief and vanity.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Of oaths his mouth is full, And deceits, and fraud: Under his tongue [is] perverseness and iniquity,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His mouth<S>6310</S> is full<S>4390</S> of cursing<S>423</S> and deceit<S>4820</S> and oppression<S>8496</S>: Under his tongue<S>3956</S> is mischief<S>5999</S> and iniquity<S>205</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">His mouth is full of cursing, deceit, and oppression. Under his tongue is mischief and iniquity. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:8</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He sitteth in the lurking places of the villages: in the secret places doth he murder the innocent: his eyes are privily set against the poor.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He doth sit in an ambush of the villages, In secret places he doth slay the innocent. His eyes for the afflicted watch secretly,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He sitteth<S>3427</S> in the lurking-places<S>3993</S> of the villages<S>2691</S>; In the secret places<S>3993</S> doth he murder<S>2026</S> the innocent<S>5355</S>; His eyes<S>5869</S> are privily set<S>6845</S> against the helpless<S>2489</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He lies in wait near the villages. From ambushes, he murders the innocent. His eyes are secretly set against the helpless. </span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:9</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He lieth in wait secretly as a lion in his den: he lieth in wait to catch the poor: he doth catch the poor, when he draweth him into his net.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He lieth in wait in a secret place, as a lion in a covert. He lieth in wait to catch the poor, He catcheth the poor, drawing him into his net.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He lurketh<S>693</S> in secret<S>4565</S> as a lion<S>738</S> in his covert<S>5520</S>; He lieth in wait<S>693</S> to catch<S>2414</S> the poor<S>6041</S>: He doth catch<S>2414</S> the poor<S>6041</S>, when he draweth<S>4900</S> him in his net<S>7568</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He lurks in secret as a lion in his ambush. He lies in wait to catch the helpless. He catches the helpless, when he draws him in his net. </span></div>
