            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Psalms 10:10</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He croucheth, and humbleth himself, that the poor may fall by his strong ones.</span></div>
