              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">He croucheth<S>1794</S>, he boweth<S>7817</S> down<S>2489</S>, And the helpless fall<S>5307</S> by his strong ones<S>6099</S>.</span></div>
